name: Donate to Children's Cancer Foundation
description: This Christmas, give a little love... For just $10, you will be buying a medium ToFu Oyako cooling towel worth $25.90 for the little ones of Children's Cancer Foundation. Going through the harsh and torturous cancer treatment would often result in skin irritation, fever and many other ailments. Our cooling towels would be able to comfort them... just a little but even that would go a long way in encouraging them to fight on! With the oh too cute ToFu designs, they will also be lifting the spirits of the children! So fight on with them.. and give a little love!

About tokidoki

tokidoki, which translates as “sometimes” in Japanese, is the vision of Italian artist Simone Legno and his partners, serial entrepreneurs Pooneh Mohajer and Ivan Arnold. Since debuting in 2005, tokidoki has amassed a cult-like following for its larger-than-life characters and emerged as a sought-after global lifestyle brand. This innovative company is known not only for its eye-popping aesthetic and criminally cute characters but also its megawatt partnerships with the likes of mega brands such as, Hello Kitty, Karl Lagerfeld, LeSportsac, Barbie, Onitsuka Tiger, Marvel and others
